Joe Duttine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joe_Duttine 0 Joe Duttine, sometimes credited as Jo Duttine, is an English film, theatre and television actor. He currently plays Tim Metcalfe in Coronation Street. He is also known for his role in Shameless as Cameron Donnelly the father of Maxine.
